# Quick Start Guide ðŸš€

Get your Personal Productivity Brain up and running in 5 minutes!

## Step 1: Install Dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

## Step 2: Get Tambo API Key

### Option A: Tambo Cloud (Easiest)
1. Visit [tambo.co](https://tambo.co)
2. Sign up for a free account
3. Create a project
4. Copy your API key

### Option B: Self-Hosted
```bash
npx tambo init
# Select "Self-hosted" and follow Docker setup instructions
```

## Step 3: Configure Environment
```bash
# Create environment file
cp .env.example .env.local

# Edit .env.local and add your API key
NEXT_PUBLIC_TAMBO_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
```

## Step 4: Run the App
```bash
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) in your browser!

## Step 5: Add Sample Data (Optional)

1. Open browser console (F12)
2. Copy the contents of `seed-data.js`
3. Paste into console
4. Run: `seedProductivityBrain()`
5. Refresh the page

